Introduction
------------
This repo contains the Arduino sketch that runs the instrument pack for Mark and Katherine's Stratoballoon project.  For detailed construction information, please visit http://markegilbert.wordpress.com/category/science/, and look for the numerous podcasts and blog posts starting October 22, 2012.


Compilation
-----------
1) Download the code

2) Place the libraries/OneWire folder in your arduino library.
	On your Mac:: In (home directory)/Documents/Arduino/libraries
	On your PC:: My Documents -> Arduino -> libraries
	On your Linux box: (home directory)/sketchbook/libraries

3) Open the Balloon/Balloon.ino sketch and compile it..

